@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_nwurod(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (0.65 + (0.20 - (v0 + 0.55 - v1 + 0.56)))
    tmp = 0.93
    v1 = wp.exp(0.45)
    tmp = v0
    tmp = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.89 * v0 + 0.72)) * (v2 / wp.exp(v2 + 0.83)))
    v0 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
